  apply Arrow.hom_ext
  ¬∑ apply sq‚ÇÅ‚ÇÇ.isPushout.hom_ext
    all_goals simp
  ¬∑ simp

/-- Given a `PushoutObjObj` of `f‚ÇÅ : Arrow C‚ÇÅ` and `f‚ÇÇ : Arrow C‚ÇÇ`, a `PushoutObjObj` of `f‚ÇÅ'` and
