    (ofHasPullback G f‚ÇÅ f‚ÇÉ).œÄ =
    (IsPullback.of_hasPullback ((G.obj (op X‚ÇÅ)).map f‚ÇÉ) ((G.map f‚ÇÅ.op).app Y‚ÇÉ)).lift
